Episode 1:

    This resource has been so helpful in regard to getting OpenGL to work with the Win32 API:
    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/45518843/initializing-opengl-without-libraries

    Glossary of Win32 Window Types:
        HGLRC     - OpenGL Rendering Context
        HDC       - Handle to a Device Context
        HWND      - Handle to a Window
        HINSTANCE - Handle to this program's instance
        WNDCLASSA - Window Class (A for ANSI)